.1</span> 標題：斗、撒頓（saton）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σάτον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： saton)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:33\">MAT 13:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:21\">LUK 13:21</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:33\">MAT 13:33</a> ：這裡具體是多少麵粉並不重要，不過譯本一般會表明數量相對較大。翻譯者有時會把“three measures”（「三量器」；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）譯作「三容器」或三個當地常用的對等量度，比如「三盤」。另外，翻譯者也可以選用當地大約50磅或40升麵粉的計量方式，例如「一蒲式耳」（“a bushel”； <abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）。通俗譯本會避免使用具體的體積數。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 作“three big batches”（「三大團」），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 作“a large tub”（「一大盆」），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"God&#x27;s Word Translation\">GW</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Italian Common Language Version\">ITCL</abbr> 僅僅說“a large amount”（「很多」）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
