.3</span> 標題：升（choinix）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： χοῖνιξ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： choinix)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:6\">REV 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:6\">REV 6:6</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:6\">REV 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:6\">REV 6:6</a> ：<em>choinix</em> 約等於一升或一夸脫，可以不必更改數值而直接替換。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
